    <title>우분투(Ubuntu) 18.04 도커(Docker) 설치</title>
    <link href="https://sengwoolee.dev/2020/03/29/inital%20post/"/>
    <id>https://sengwoolee.dev/2020/03/29/inital%20post/</id>
    <published>2020-03-29T06:17:21.403Z</published>
